description: This coverage shows spatial extent of selected Land use cover classes in 2005 for the WIO. This land cover data documents how much the WIO region within a 100 km coastal buffer is covered by Rainfed cropland, irrigated or post flooded land and Urban areas. This data coverage is a derived product from European Space Agency land-use cover class global land cover maps at 300m spatial resolution.
name: WIO Urban areas 2005
